449
00:19:39,350 --> 00:19:40,140
You can handle it.

450
00:19:40,160 --> 00:19:40,770
Come with me!

451
00:19:40,790 --> 00:19:41,620
Wei Xiaoxi!

452
00:19:41,640 --> 00:19:43,220
