473
00:20:29,510 --> 00:20:30,420
No signs of infection.

474
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:31,730
Leave it to me, go take care of others.

475
00:20:38,750 --> 00:20:39,460
Ms. Zhou,

476
00:20:39,960 --> 00:20:40,980
