483
00:21:02,030 --> 00:21:03,180
Intubation isn't an option for now.

484
00:21:03,920 --> 00:21:04,900
Give him oxygen first.

485
00:21:04,920 --> 00:21:05,900
My rough estimate,

486
00:21:05,920 --> 00:21:07,420
there are at least a dozen shrapnel pieces

487
00:21:07,440 --> 00:21:08,620
deep in his chest cavity.

488
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:18,010
Pneumothorax.

489
00:21:18,440 --> 00:21:19,940
Apply pressure dressing, prepare for surgery.

490
00:21:19,960 --> 00:21:20,770
Test results are in.

491
00:21:23,030 --> 00:21:24,090
