502
00:21:43,160 --> 00:21:43,980
A black tank top.

503
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:45,460
Yellow hair, short guy.

504
00:21:45,590 --> 00:21:46,420
Have you seen him?

505
00:21:47,270 --> 00:21:48,180
Is it that guy?

506
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:49,660
The one with a hole in his chest?

507
00:21:53,440 --> 00:21:55,290
