508
00:21:55,310 --> 00:21:57,380
Then, we'll do a closed chest drainage procedure.

509
00:21:58,160 --> 00:21:59,420
This should temporarily manage the pneumothorax.

510
00:22:00,350 --> 00:22:01,570
I've asked Wei Xiaoxi to monitor him.

511
00:22:01,590 --> 00:22:03,420
Keeping a close watch on his drainage status.

512
00:22:05,750 --> 00:22:07,330
Now, all we need is blood.

513
00:22:08,920 --> 00:22:11,570
Rh-negative blood can't be sourced on short notice.

514
00:22:12,110 --> 00:22:13,620
The blood bank doesn't have any in stock either.

515
00:22:13,960 --> 00:22:15,620
We'll have to find a donor.

516
00:22:16,680 --> 00:22:17,490
In his condition,

517
00:22:17,510 --> 00:22:19,220
