528
00:22:45,920 --> 00:22:47,420
Guo Xuan's makeup artist.

529
00:22:47,640 --> 00:22:48,660
We've met before.

530
00:22:50,400 --> 00:22:51,900
I remember you, Taozi.

531
00:22:52,680 --> 00:22:53,730
Ding Zhike is your...

532
00:22:53,750 --> 00:22:54,810
I'm his girlfriend.

533
00:22:55,110 --> 00:22:56,220
How is he?

534
00:22:56,750 --> 00:22:57,980
