540
00:23:09,720 --> 00:23:11,980
He has Rh-negative blood, it's rare.

541
00:23:12,000 --> 00:23:13,290
The blood bank doesn't have any.

542
00:23:13,310 --> 00:23:14,460
R what blood?

543
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:15,860
Isn't he type A?

544
00:23:16,070 --> 00:23:18,330
He's type A, but Rh-negative.

545
00:23:18,350 --> 00:23:19,810
It's commonly known as "panda blood."

546
00:23:20,030 --> 00:23:21,330
Only a matching donor

547
00:23:21,350 --> 00:23:22,460
can save him.

548
00:23:22,480 --> 00:23:22,900
That's right.

549
00:23:22,920 --> 00:23:25,900
