550
00:23:26,000 --> 00:23:28,140
I don't have his family's contact info.

551
00:23:28,590 --> 00:23:29,900
But I can check his phone.

552
00:23:30,510 --> 00:23:32,570
Does he have any family in Rongchuan?

553
00:23:33,590 --> 00:23:34,290
No.

554
00:23:35,070 --> 00:23:36,140
His family is in Shaanxi.

555
00:23:36,160 --> 00:23:37,620
Only he and his brother moved out.

556
00:23:38,160 --> 00:23:40,180
His brother got married last year and returned home.

557
00:23:40,920 --> 00:23:42,620
Let's focus on finding a donor first.

558
00:23:43,510 --> 00:23:45,180
Can I see him?

559
00:23:46,350 --> 00:23:47,180
Not yet.

560
00:23:48,350 --> 00:23:49,810
He's in isolation and under intensive care.

561
00:23:49,830 --> 00:23:52,050
We're also waiting for blood before we can operate.

562
00:23:54,590 --> 00:23:55,660
Will he die?

563
00:23:59,400 --> 00:24:00,460
Alright.

564
00:24:00,550 --> 00:24:01,490
Be careful.

565
00:24:02,920 --> 00:24:04,010
Check when they'll arrive.

566
00:24:04,160 --> 00:24:04,730
Got it.

567
00:24:06,510 --> 00:24:07,490
Keep up!

568
00:24:08,680 --> 00:24:09,140
Alright.

569
00:24:17,680 --> 00:24:18,570
Double-check everything.

570
00:24:35,350 --> 00:24:36,250
