00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:56,900
I fell.

574
00:24:59,270 --> 00:25:00,420
Your wound is irregular

575
00:25:00,440 --> 00:25:01,530
and has lacerations.

576
00:25:01,750 --> 00:25:03,730
It must have been caused by a large dog

577
00:25:03,750 --> 00:25:04,860
with a strong bite force.

578
00:25:05,680 --> 00:25:07,460
Even if the dog was vaccinated,

579
00:25:08,310 --> 00:25:10,460
you still have a risk of rabies infection.

580
00:25:11,920 --> 00:25:14,380
Honestly, repairing this wound isn't difficult,

581
00:25:15,160 --> 00:25:16,660
but you must tell me the truth

582
00:25:16,960 --> 00:25:18,290
so I can provide the right treatment.

583
00:25:21,640 --> 00:25:23,620
Beds five and six have relatively small burn areas.

584
00:25:23,640 --> 00:25:25,700
We have performed cooling and pain management.

585
00:25:26,310 --> 00:25:27,810
Bed seven has a larger burn area,

586
00:25:28,160 --> 00:25:30,090
third-degree burns on the palm, second-degree burns on the arm.

587
00:25:31,030 --> 00:25:31,700
Ms. Zhou,

588
00:25:32,200 --> 00:25:33,530
none of them are leaving today.

589
00:25:33,960 --> 00:25:35,660
Everyone, just follow Ms. Zhou's instructions, okay?

590
00:25:35,680 --> 00:25:36,810
Alright. Don't worry.

591
00:25:36,830 --> 00:25:37,900
Thank you, guys.

592
00:25:38,160 --> 00:25:39,660
The key is postoperative care.

593
00:25:39,680 --> 00:25:40,660
We must prevent shock,

594
00:25:40,680 --> 00:25:42,180
keep the airway clear,

595
00:25:42,350 --> 00:25:43,140
and remove necrotic tissue

596
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:45,330
when changing the dressing.

597
00:25:46,160 --> 00:25:48,180
Fluid replacement, infection control, and symptomatic treatment.

598
00:25:48,310 --> 00:25:49,700
Thank you.

599
00:25:49,830 --> 00:25:50,460
Lu,

600
00:25:50,480 --> 00:25:51,860
I'll leave the staffing arrangements to you.

601
00:25:51,880 --> 00:25:52,460
Got it.

602
00:26:04,310 --> 00:26:05,900
Dr. Wei, go grab a meal first.

603
00:26:05,920 --> 00:26:06,810
I'll watch over things for you.

604
00:26:10,790 --> 00:26:12,460
It's fine. I'll handle it myself. Don't worry.

605
00:26:15,110 --> 00:26:17,090
The wound on his upper right chest

606
00:26:17,110 --> 00:26:18,700
has a diameter of about thirteen centimeters.

607
00:26:19,750 --> 00:26:20,380
In his condition,

608
00:26:20,400 --> 00:26:22,380
we should consider a lower abdominal flap transplant.

609
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:24,460
Lower abdomen?

610
00:26:25,110 --> 00:26:26,010
Will it be enough to cover?

611
00:26:26,960 --> 00:26:27,810
More or less.

612
00:26:28,480 --> 00:26:29,330
I think

613
00:26:29,720 --> 00:26:31,050
the anterolateral thigh flap

614
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:32,050
is large enough in area.

615
00:26:32,510 --> 00:26:34,490
But it would require microsurgical anastomosis.

616
00:26:35,830 --> 00:26:37,010
The thigh area is sufficient,

617
00:26:37,310 --> 00:26:38,330
but like you said,

618
00:26:38,350 --> 00:26:39,700
we would still need to do vascular anastomosis,

619
00:26:40,440 --> 00:26:41,980
which makes the procedure more complex.

620
00:26:42,640 --> 00:26:44,660
And there's also the risk of flap necrosis.

621
00:26:46,880 --> 00:26:49,700
What worries me the most right now is the blood supply.

622
00:26:49,720 --> 00:26:51,290
Rh-negative...

623
00:26:52,110 --> 00:26:54,090
I've sent out requests for help in all my circles,

624
00:26:54,110 --> 00:26:55,140
but there's no response.

625
00:26:55,720 --> 00:26:57,220
The hospital is experiencing

626
00:26:57,240 --> 00:26:58,140
a severe blood shortage right now,

627
00:26:58,590 --> 00:27:00,770
especially for his rare blood type.

628
00:27:02,640 --> 00:27:03,980
Did you admit Ding Zhike?

629
00:27:04,350 --> 00:27:05,010
Yes.

630
00:27:05,960 --> 00:27:06,810
The police are looking for you.

631
00:27:07,960 --> 00:27:09,770
Can you determine what caused this?

632
00:27:10,240 --> 00:27:11,940
Based on the wound,

633
00:27:11,960 --> 00:27:13,940
the possibility of a close-range explosion is higher.

634
00:27:15,750 --> 00:27:16,330
Alright.

635
00:27:17,160 --> 00:27:18,860
We have understood the basic situation.

636
00:27:19,030 --> 00:27:20,220
Thank you for your cooperation.

637
00:27:20,440 --> 00:27:21,730
If Ding Zhike wakes up,

638
00:27:21,750 --> 00:27:22,900
please notify us immediately.

639
00:27:23,830 --> 00:27:25,050
Come, this way, please.

640
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:30,570
Taozi,

641
00:27:32,240 --> 00:27:33,810
what did the police want with you just now?

642
00:27:33,830 --> 00:27:35,730
They just wanted to understand the situation.

643
00:27:35,750 --> 00:27:36,860
I just want to ask you one thing,

644
00:27:37,240 --> 00:27:38,900
Was it Ding who caused the fire?

645
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:40,010
It wasn't him.

646
00:27:40,030 --> 00:27:41,050
He's in charge of fire.

647
00:27:41,070 --> 00:27:41,700
He was the closest to it.

648
00:27:41,720 --> 00:27:43,140
If it wasn't him, who else was it? Tell me.

649
00:27:43,160 --> 00:27:44,220
It really wasn't him.

650
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:45,900
It definitely was him.

651
00:27:45,920 --> 00:27:47,420
It had to be him. Otherwise, why would the police look for him?

652
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:48,140
No.

653
00:27:48,160 --> 00:27:49,570
We just wanna understand the truth of the situation.

654
00:27:49,590 --> 00:27:50,420
Is that so hard?

655
00:27:50,440 --> 00:27:51,250
It wasn't him.

656
00:27:51,440 --> 00:27:52,460
Look at my leg.

657
00:27:52,480 --> 00:27:53,330
It's all injured like this.

658
00:27:53,350 --> 00:27:54,530
Will I ever be able to marry a wife?

659
00:27:54,550 --> 00:27:55,530
Look at my hands.

660
00:27:55,550 --> 00:27:57,050
It'll take at least half a year to heal.

661
00:27:57,070 --> 00:27:57,980
At least half a year.

662
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:58,810
Am I not going to work?

663
00:27:58,830 --> 00:28:00,330
Alright.

664
00:28:00,350 --> 00:28:02,050
I understand everyone's mood.

665
00:28:02,070 --> 00:28:03,250
But the police investigation results

666
00:28:03,270 --> 00:28:05,050
haven't come out yet, right?

667
00:28:05,240 --> 00:28:06,490
This fire wasn't started by her.

668
00:28:06,510 --> 00:28:06,770
Right?

669
00:28:06,790 --> 00:28:08,290
You're getting angry at a young girl,

670
00:28:08,310 --> 00:28:09,620
but that's not gonna solve the problem.

671
00:28:09,880 --> 00:28:11,770
The most important thing for you right now

672
00:28:11,790 --> 00:28:12,860
is to return to your rooms,

673
00:28:13,030 --> 00:28:14,980
get some good rest, and focus on your recovery.

674
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:15,770
Alright?

675
00:28:15,960 --> 00:28:17,420
Why are you just standing around?

676
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:18,220
Go back to your rooms.

677
00:28:18,350 --> 00:28:19,330
If I don't work,

678
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:20,620
how am I supposed to live?

679
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:21,730
Am I supposed to just live on air?

680
00:28:21,750 --> 00:28:22,940
Sleep well.

681
00:28:22,960 --> 00:28:24,180
Your injuries will heal faster.

682
00:28:24,400 --> 00:28:25,090
Seriously...

683
00:28:31,350 --> 00:28:32,140
Ms. Qiao,

684
00:28:32,510 --> 00:28:33,380
let's have a small meeting.

685
00:28:35,110 --> 00:28:35,900
Stop crying.

686
00:28:39,550 --> 00:28:41,380
The police are still investigating.

687
00:28:41,400 --> 00:28:42,620
You're already accusing him.

688
00:28:42,640 --> 00:28:43,570
Now you wanna transfer him?

689
00:28:43,880 --> 00:28:45,090
That's not necessary.

690
00:28:45,240 --> 00:28:46,860
It wasn't necessary before.

691
00:28:47,270 --> 00:28:48,460
Since you've been here,

692
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:49,980
it's been quite lively around here.

693
00:28:50,270 --> 00:28:51,460
Let me count for you.

694
00:28:51,830 --> 00:28:53,860
Jiang Rong, Hao Xin, Lin Qiang,

695
00:28:54,110 --> 00:28:55,660
and now we've added an arsonist.

696
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:58,700
Are you afraid that Gemu doesn't have enough money for trending topics?

697
00:28:58,720 --> 00:29:00,900
Look at how much advertising money I've saved for you.

698
00:29:01,310 --> 00:29:02,010
Besides,

699
00:29:02,270 --> 00:29:04,010
this just proves my natural talent.

700
00:29:04,270 --> 00:29:05,330
Whatever I do, it turns into a hit.

701
00:29:06,550 --> 00:29:07,700
Personally, I don't mind.

702
00:29:07,720 --> 00:29:09,380
At worst, it's just some PR trouble.

703
00:29:09,960 --> 00:29:12,730
But Gemu image can't take so much turmoil.

704
00:29:13,720 --> 00:29:15,420
Ding Zhike is still in danger.

705
00:29:15,440 --> 00:29:16,940
We should save him first.

706
00:29:17,440 --> 00:29:18,940
If he suddenly passes away now,

707
00:29:18,960 --> 00:29:20,490
how much damage would that do to Gemu's image?

708
00:29:20,510 --> 00:29:21,980
Yes, we wanna save him.

709
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:23,530
But we still can't find the blood.

710
00:29:23,550 --> 00:29:24,490
There's nothing we can do about that.

711
00:29:25,480 --> 00:29:26,660
Sorry, I'm late.

712
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:28,530
I have something to tell you.

713
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:49,980
Meng Haoran?

714
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:50,900
Is it really him?

715
00:29:51,480 --> 00:29:53,010
You recognize him even wrapped up like that?

716
00:29:53,030 --> 00:29:54,010
It's definitely him.

717
00:29:54,030 --> 00:29:54,860
Look at this picture.

718
00:29:55,070 --> 00:29:55,940
Look at this one.

719
00:29:56,070 --> 00:29:56,660
See?

720
00:29:56,680 --> 00:29:58,730
He's been wearing that hat for over a hundred years.

721
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:00,620
Who are you talking about?

722
00:30:01,200 --> 00:30:02,660
Meng Haoran.

723
00:30:02,920 --> 00:30:04,460
The male team leader.

724
00:30:04,720 --> 00:30:07,050
He was already acting in major productions when he debuted.

725
00:30:07,070 --> 00:30:08,730
The very crew that caught fire today,

726
00:30:09,440 --> 00:30:11,250
he was visiting colleagues there.

727
00:30:12,200 --> 00:30:13,140
Who told you that?

728
00:30:13,160 --> 00:30:14,810
He went straight to the VIP ward.

729
00:30:15,590 --> 00:30:16,330
Guo Xuan.

730
00:30:16,550 --> 00:30:17,700
No one saw you, right?

731
00:30:27,830 --> 00:30:29,620
I've said it's fine.

732
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,380
Is Duke alright?

733
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:32,770
I had Xiao Xu take him home.

734
00:30:33,240 --> 00:30:34,860
He'll get a good scolding when we get back.

735
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:36,660
But it's not its fault.

736
00:30:36,920 --> 00:30:39,180
He's usually very well-behaved and obedient.

737
00:30:39,200 --> 00:30:40,660
He's never hurt anyone.

738
00:30:40,680 --> 00:30:41,900
With all that noise,

739
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:43,940
he was frightened.

740
00:30:44,790 --> 00:30:45,700
Does it still hurt?

741
00:30:54,790 --> 00:30:56,700
My injury is fine now.

742
00:30:56,720 --> 00:30:57,860
You should head back quickly.

743
00:30:58,160 --> 00:30:59,730
If we get caught on camera, it'll be troublesome.

744
00:31:00,270 --> 00:31:01,220
It's fine if we get caught.

745
00:31:01,400 --> 00:31:02,290
It'll drive Fang Yu crazy.

746
00:31:02,880 --> 00:31:04,050
And then you'll marry me.

747
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:08,140
Meng Haoran,

748
00:31:08,510 --> 00:31:09,860
get a grip.

749
00:31:10,640 --> 00:31:11,860
If this thing blows up,

750
00:31:11,880 --> 00:31:13,290
you'll be the one who gets trouble, and I'll be the one who gets scolded.

751
00:31:13,310 --> 00:31:14,570
We're both finished.

752
00:31:15,550 --> 00:31:16,330
Hurry up and leave.

753
00:31:17,240 --> 00:31:18,570
Just looking at you for one more second annoys me.

754
00:31:20,440 --> 00:31:21,570
It's always like this.

755
00:31:22,830 --> 00:31:24,090
Like we're doing something wrong.

756
00:31:24,720 --> 00:31:26,140
Go look at the people from the crew.

757
00:31:26,160 --> 00:31:27,380
If they're caught on camera, at least they have an excuse.

758
00:31:29,790 --> 00:31:31,180
Hat, glasses, mask.

759
00:31:37,680 --> 00:31:38,700
Is this better now?

760
00:31:52,400 --> 00:31:53,220
Meng!

761
00:32:08,240 --> 00:32:08,940
Meng!

762
00:32:09,880 --> 00:32:11,420
Meng!

763
00:32:18,030 --> 00:32:19,420
Guo Xuan is in our hospital?

764
00:32:19,920 --> 00:32:20,730
What happened to her?

765
00:32:21,160 --> 00:32:22,010
Animal bite.

766
00:32:22,110 --> 00:32:23,660
Nothing serious, I've already treated it.

767
00:32:23,680 --> 00:32:24,420
Great.

768
00:32:24,790 --> 00:32:26,250
One is a top host,

769
00:32:26,880 --> 00:32:27,860
the other is an arsonist.

770
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:31,290
Gemu has two ticking time bombs.

771
00:32:31,510 --> 00:32:34,290
If you ask me, we should transfer Ding Zhike as soon as possible.

772
00:32:35,880 --> 00:32:37,250
So Guo Xuan's case can be kept confidential,

773
00:32:37,270 --> 00:32:38,810
but Ding Zhike has to be transferred?

774
00:32:38,830 --> 00:32:39,900
What kind of logic is that?

775
00:32:40,200 --> 00:32:41,700
I'm just considering the patient's well-being.

776
00:32:41,830 --> 00:32:43,250
We're just a specialty hospital,

777
00:32:43,270 --> 00:32:44,530
our capabilities are indeed limited.

778
00:32:45,550 --> 00:32:47,220
It's not about doubting your abilities.

779
00:32:47,240 --> 00:32:49,250
The transfer won't trouble you or Ms. Zhou.

780
00:32:49,270 --> 00:32:50,010
I'll handle it.

781
00:32:50,240 --> 00:32:51,980
He has an open pneumothorax right now.

782
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:54,140
This often leads to hemothorax.

783
00:32:54,310 --> 00:32:55,010
Hemothorax?

784
00:32:55,310 --> 00:32:56,490
That means internal bleeding in the wound.

785
00:32:56,720 --> 00:32:57,770
If he goes into shockand

786
00:32:57,790 --> 00:32:58,730
we don't have blood ready,

787
00:32:58,750 --> 00:33:00,010
he'll be beyond saving.

788
00:33:01,400 --> 00:33:02,770
This situation is too dangerous.

789
00:33:02,790 --> 00:33:04,050
I absolutely do not agree to the transfer.

790
00:33:04,070 --> 00:33:06,090
You were the one who said surgery must be done within eight hours, right?

791
00:33:07,480 --> 00:33:08,530
There are five hours left.

792
00:33:08,550 --> 00:33:10,090
Without blood, how can we operate?

793
00:33:11,480 --> 00:33:12,380
The blood bank just called.

794
00:33:12,400 --> 00:33:13,290
We found the blood.

795
00:33:13,310 --> 00:33:14,290
The donor is from Shanghai.

796
00:33:14,310 --> 00:33:15,620
The fastest they can arrive is four hours.

797
00:33:16,750 --> 00:33:17,900
Five hours is more than enough.

798
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:18,770
Let's go!

799
00:33:56,160 --> 00:33:57,770
The pacing is too slow overall.

800
00:33:57,790 --> 00:33:59,220
Tighten up the edits for me.

801
00:33:59,720 --> 00:34:01,570
Can't you find more footage?

802
00:34:01,750 --> 00:34:03,140
You're editing an operation video,

803
00:34:03,160 --> 00:34:04,660
do you think it has any tension?

804
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:05,660
Duke.

805
00:34:08,280 --> 00:34:09,340
Stop barking, Duke.

806
00:34:10,510 --> 00:34:11,130
Come here.

807
00:34:16,280 --> 00:34:16,900
Duke.

808
00:34:18,550 --> 00:34:20,010
Go away!

809
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:21,530
Go away!

810
00:34:24,000 --> 00:34:24,860
Are you okay, Xuan?

811
00:34:24,880 --> 00:34:25,460
Come on.

812
00:34:26,110 --> 00:34:27,860
Someone!

813
00:34:48,150 --> 00:34:48,780
Ms. Qiao,

814
00:34:49,710 --> 00:34:50,740
I've been closely monitoring

815
00:34:50,760 --> 00:34:51,820
as you instructed.

816
00:34:51,840 --> 00:34:53,530
Recording every half hour.

817
00:34:53,550 --> 00:34:55,090
Continuous oxygen at one liter per minute.

818
00:34:55,110 --> 00:34:57,170
His vital signs are all stable.

819
00:34:57,190 --> 00:34:58,170
No abnormal breathing.

820
00:34:58,190 --> 00:34:59,980
No changes in the drainage fluid.

821
00:35:01,920 --> 00:35:03,260
The next four hours are the most critical.

822
00:35:03,280 --> 00:35:04,300
You absolutely cannot let your guard down.

823
00:35:04,320 --> 00:35:05,570
Especially with the drainage.

824
00:35:05,590 --> 00:35:07,050
If anything unusual happens, call me immediately.

825
00:35:07,480 --> 00:35:08,010
Stay alert.

826
00:35:08,030 --> 00:35:09,530
Stop acting like you're half-asleep all the time.

827
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:15,210
Dr. Wei,

828
00:35:15,880 --> 00:35:17,690
you've already done a great job.

829
00:35:17,960 --> 00:35:19,610
This was our responsibility.

830
00:35:19,630 --> 00:35:21,050
Everyone sees your effort.

831
00:35:21,550 --> 00:35:22,170
Keep going!

832
00:35:31,550 --> 00:35:32,170
Doctor,

833
00:35:32,670 --> 00:35:34,340
are you planning to stop treating him?

834
00:35:34,590 --> 00:35:35,420
Who told you that?

835
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:37,530
The fire has nothing to do with Ding Zhike.

836
00:35:37,550 --> 00:35:38,940
He was framed.

837
00:35:38,960 --> 00:35:40,980
His personal information has been dug up online.

838
00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:43,380
They're saying he caused the explosion and fire by smoking,

839
00:35:43,400 --> 00:35:44,690
he doesn't deserve to be saved.

840
00:35:44,710 --> 00:35:46,170
But it really wasn't his fault!

841
00:35:46,190 --> 00:35:47,380
Pealse!

842
00:35:47,630 --> 00:35:48,900
Saving lives is our duty.

843
00:35:49,320 --> 00:35:50,380
What they say doesn't matter.

844
00:35:56,590 --> 00:35:58,300
Dog bites are usually irregular.

845
00:35:58,440 --> 00:35:59,860
The wounds are hard to treat.

846
00:36:00,440 --> 00:36:01,900
Especially in areas with a lot of movement,

847
00:36:01,920 --> 00:36:03,090
the tension here is quite high.

848
00:36:03,400 --> 00:36:06,090
Whether the scar heals as expected

849
00:36:06,110 --> 00:36:08,210
depends on your post-op tension-reducing care.

850
00:36:08,670 --> 00:36:10,860
I'd say you need to stay hospitalized for at least a week.

851
00:36:11,590 --> 00:36:12,900
But don't worry.

